flowchart TD
    A[Start run: user submits query] --> B[POST /api/agents/run]
    B --> C{API result}
    C -->|error| D[Show deterministic run error\nKeep query for retry]
    C -->|success| E[Store runDetails + output]
    E --> F{graph_state.timeline present?}
    F -->|yes| G[Render ordered timeline steps]
    F -->|no| H[Render 'No graph timeline available']
    E --> I{Sub-queries present?}
    I -->|yes| J[Render sub-query list with tool labels]
    I -->|no| K[Render sub-query empty state]
    E --> L{Validation results present?}
    L -->|yes| M[Render validation statuses]
    L -->|no| N[Render validation empty state]
    G --> O[Final answer + progress history coexist]
    H --> O
    J --> O
    K --> O
    M --> O
    N --> O

    P[Test/Build Validation] --> Q[Health endpoint 200]
    P --> R[Backend pytest: pass]
    P --> S[Frontend vitest: pass]
    P --> T[Frontend typecheck: pass after adding vite-env.d.ts]
    P --> U[Frontend build: pass]

    V[Blocked items] --> W[None]
